summary: My old Amelia Rose RaceMenu preset was very popular, so I figured my updated version should be posted! Here is Amelia Rose V2!
descriptionHtml:
Basically just an upgraded and updated version of my old Amelia Rose RaceMenu preset! Enjoy!

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/88004-0-1511320576.jpg[/img]
[u][b]
Installation is easy[/b][/u]
[color=#00ff00]
NMM - install normally like any other mod.

Manual - extract contents of the 7zip file > place into your main skyrim folder.

In RaceMenu, load the sculpt file, then load the preset file.[/color]

~wnisewond
author: wnisewond
